<br>
@ 1000ac I would take 41dps (ground spiders in velks)/over 100 spiders parse<br>
<br>
@ 1100ac I would take 32dps (over 400 spiders)<br>
<br>
@ 1200ac I would take 24dps (over 500 spiders)<br>
<br>
@ 1250ac I would take 21dps (300~ spiders)<br>
<br>
@ 1300ac I would take 17dps (100~)<br>
<br>
@ 1350ac I would take 15dps (100~)<br>
<br>
<br>
