if your getting hit by a flurry in ntov, then your going to see a lot better results with higher ac (more misses, better dmg mitigation)<br>
<br>
personally if im tanking i go no less than 1500 ac (buffed), it makes a huge difference, luckily i dont give up many hps with a higher ac<br>
<br>
there are a lot of variables in testing ac thou, but the best way is to test yourself, cause we will all fight different mobs, and are in different groups etc<br>
